column12: Branched optimal moiety recognized by anti-carbohydrate antibodies specific for the Group A Streptococcus cell-wall polysaccharide. The source of this trisaccharide is the cell-wall polysaccharide (CWPS) of Group A Streptococcus.
a-L-Rhap-(1-2)-[b-D-GlcpNAc-(1-3)]-a-L-Rhap-(1-3)-a-L-Rhap-(1-2)-[b-D-GlcpNAc-(1-3)]-a-L-Rhap The epitope is derived from cell-wall poly-alpha-L-rhamnopyranosyl backbone of Streptococcus Group A.
